{"type":null,"faqId":38518,"title":"更改锁屏风格","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>1.</span><a name=\"_task_pattern_unlock-chtext\"><span> </span><span>图案解锁</span></a>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125566\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“设置”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>在“全部设置”页签下，点击“锁屏和密码”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>点击“锁屏密码 &gt; 图案密码”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>连接至少四个点绘制图案，然后再次绘制图案进行确认。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>设置备用数字密码。当您忘记解锁图案时，可输入该数字密码完成解锁。</span>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<span>2.</span><a name=\"_task_pin_unlock-chtext\"><span> </span><span>数字密码解锁</span></a>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125567\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“设置”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>在“全部设置”页签下，点击“锁屏和密码”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>点击“锁屏密码 &gt; 数字密码”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>输入至少四位数字，然后再次输入进行确认。</span>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<span>3.</span><a name=\"_task_password_unlock-chtext\"><span> </span><span>混合密码解锁</span></a>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125568\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“设置”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>在“全部设置”页签下，点击“锁屏和密码”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>点击“锁屏密码 &gt; 混合密码”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>按要求输入包含至少四个字符的混合密码，然后再次输入进行确认。</span>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  ></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":143,"faqType":"系统功能与设置","useful":1,"unUseful":3,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"3798","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-System-Settings","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1441448687000,"seriesProductName":"GRA-CL00,GRA-CL10,GRA-TL00,GRA-UL00,GRA-UL10","visitedTimes":193,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"更改锁屏风格","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}